affixes.name: Fortified
affixes.description: Non-boss enemies have 20% more health and inflict up to 30% increased damage.

affixes.name: Spiteful
affixes.description: Fiends rise from the corpses of non-boss enemies and pursue random players.

affixes.name: Volcanic
affixes.description: While in combat, enemies periodically cause gouts of flame to erupt beneath the feet of distant players.

affixes.name: Prideful
affixes.description: Players overflow with pride as they defeat non-boss enemies, eventually forming a Manifestation of Pride. Defeating this Manifestation greatly empowers players.
